<h1 id="sparrowx">SparrowX</h1>

<p>A clean minimal Jekyll theme for SEO-focused writers. The theme loads fast and itâ€™s Netlify CMS-ready. SparrowX is a remix of sparrow by <a href="https://github.com/lingxz/sparrow">lingxz</a>.</p>

<p><a href="https://sparrowx.mighil.com/">Live Demo</a></p>

